comment._content: This aircraft was originally delivered to Southern Airways in 1978. After being sold to Trans Central, it went on to fly for Terre Haute, Ind. based Britt Airways. As I last saw this plane, it was based at the Hawthrone, Ca. Airport. flying for a telecommunications company.
